983Z", "title": "Marion progress", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2020236597/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2021270629/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1927", "dates": ["[1927 TO 1931]"], "description": ["Weekly Began September 22, 1927; ceased in 1931? Old Fort news was issued with the Marion progress, with separate enumeration. After ending the separate enumeration, Old Fort news continued as a column within the Marion progress. Description based on: Volume III, Number 14 (January 2, 1930); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 26, 2021). Latest issue consulted: Volume IV, Number 51 (September 17, 1931) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 26, 2021). Marion progress 2766-6301 (DLC) 2020236597 (OCoLC)1152575700"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:58.293Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2021270629/", "image_url": [], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["mcdowell", "old fort", "mcdowell county", "north carolina", "united states"], "number": ["online resource", "2766-6743", "2021270629", "2020236597", "1232927345", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division", "old fort news (old fort, n. c.) 1927-1931 [online resource]"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 53.6335, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["mcdowell", "newspapers", "old fort", "mcdowell county", "old fort (n.c.)", "north carolina", "mcdowell county (n.c.)", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:02:54.346Z", "title": "Old Fort news", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2021270629/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2017236972/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/2017236972", "https://search.catalog.loc.